data.description: Charming home with a picturesque view of the 3rd fairway at Dayton Valley Golf & Country Club. This sun-filled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom property features a cozy living room with a gas log fireplace—perfect for relaxation. From the patio, enjoy watching the golfers at the 150-yard marker. The spacious kitchen offers ample counter space and a quaint breakfast nook. Appreciate the serene golf course and mountain vistas. With a touch of TLC, this home represents a fantastic opportunity. Schedule your visit today.
